\f0\b 1. Background:
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Clinical case reports play a vital role in sharing unique clinical experiences and atypical disease phenotypes.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Extracting temporal relations between clinical events is crucial for the case report retrieval and medical question answering systems.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Existing methods face challenges in capturing global relational dependencies and require extensive feature engineering.\
