\f0\b 3. Proposed Method: CTRL-PG
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The proposed method, CTRL-PG, aims to address the limitations of existing approaches by leveraging Probabilistic Soft Logic (PSL) rules.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}By incorporating PSL regularization and global inference, CTRL-PG offers a novel framework for precise extraction of temporal relations in medical text.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\ul Motivation\ulnone : enhance the efficiency and accuracy of temporal relation extraction, enabling more advanced applications in healthcare and medical research.\
